About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in """"Gokuldham Co-operative Society"""" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - Promoolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: Deep Sea Fishing in Miami (Dolphin, Wahoo, Amberjacks, and Tripletail)
snippet.description:
In this episode of BlacktipH, I go fishing for dolphin (mahi-mahi), tripletail, wahoo, and amberjacks in Miami with the LandH Sport Fishing boat. The day started with us trolling planers and searching for floating debris. After catching a few bonito and mahi, we finally found some good floating debris. There was a bunch of tripletail on the debris. Both Laurel and I had a blast catching them. After catching the tripletail, we trolled planers around the debris and caught several wahoo. On our search for more floating debris, we found a huge school of mahi and boated over 20 fish. Towards the end of the day, Laurel caught the largest dolphin, a 20lb bull! On the way back into Miami, we stopped at a deep wreck and dropped down live baits for amberjack. Immediately I was hooked up to a giant! After an intense fight, I landed the 50+lb amberjack. Laurel finished the day with anther big amberjack!

Ten years ago, Criterion Games released their critically acclaimed franchise debut Need for Speed Hot Pursuit. It introduced NFS and racing fans to the winding, open roads of Seacrest County, Criterion‚Äôs renowned feel for breakneck speed and gameplay, and the innovative Autolog system, empowering true social competition between friends. 

Ever since, we‚Äôve heard so many stories about the triumphant moments and heated rivalries Autolog fostered. Some of which run very, very deep. Like the one between Michael and Joseph. 

Now, it‚Äôs your turn to feel the thrill of the chase and the rush of escape in NFS Hot Pursuit Remastered, arriving to PlayStation¬Æ4, Xbox One, and PC on November 6, and to Nintendo Switch‚Ñ¢ on November 13! 

Unleash a savage sense of speed both as an outlaw and a cop in this timeless racing experience updated for today‚Äôs platforms. With cross-platform multiplayer and Autolog, enhanced visuals, all main DLC delivered at launch, and much more, this is the ultimate version of Criterion Games‚Äô critically acclaimed Need for Speed debut.

Pre-order now: https://www.ea.com/games/need-for-speed/need-for-speed-hot-pursuit-remastered/buy

About Need for Speed Hot Pursuit Remastered:

RACE YOUR FRIENDS WITH CROSS-PLAY AND AUTOLOG ‚Äì Bolt down the winding Seacrest County roads headfirst in racing that is socially competitive at its core ‚Äì now with cross-play support between PS4, Xbox One, PC, and Nintendo Switch! The groundbreaking Autolog connects you and your friends in head-to-head pursuits and races and instinctively delivers challenges based on your friends‚Äô activities.

ENJOY LOADS OF EXTRA CONTENT AND UPDATES ‚Äì Get all the additional main DLC delivered at launch including an extra six hours of gameplay and more than 30 challenges. Brand new achievements, wraps, car colors, reduced hard stops, an updated photo mode and gallery, and multiple quality of life updates create an even more well-rounded gameplay experience. 

DRIVE EXOTIC SUPERCARS WITH WEAPONS ‚Äì Drive the world‚Äôs most desirable supercars on both sides of the law. Bust suspects in supercharged cop interceptors enhanced with tactical weaponry, or level the playing field with counterattacks and defensive maneuvers as an elite racer. Strategize to gain an edge over the competition, no matter what side you‚Äôre on!

CHASE AND ESCAPE TOGETHER OR SOLO ‚Äì A deep and fully-defined single-player career delivers the action of both cops and racers, with a seamlessly linked multiplayer experience across all race modes. Take on friends or play through the career solo to earn Bounty and unlock new cars, weapons, and equipment.

EXPERIENCE A TIMELESS RACING GAME WITH ENHANCED VISUALS ‚Äì Need for Speed‚Ñ¢ Hot Pursuit Remastered delivers a timeless racing experience updated for today‚Äôs generation of hardware with enhanced visuals. Play in up to 4K/60 FPS and enjoy improvements such as higher-res models, shadows, and reflections, more objects and props, longer draw distance, boosted textures, more particles, and improved AA/SSAO.

Noel offers revealing insights into the album‚Äôs universally loved singles ‚ÄòWonderwall‚Äô, ‚ÄòDon‚Äôt Look Back In Anger‚Äô, ‚ÄòRoll With It‚Äô, and ‚ÄòSome Might Say‚Äô plus album tracks including ‚ÄòShe‚Äôs Electric‚Äô, ‚ÄòMorning Glory‚Äô, and ‚ÄòChampagne Supernova‚Äô which are anthems known to generations of music fans.  Noel also discusses the single‚Äôs classic B-sides, including ‚ÄòThe Masterplan‚Äô, ‚ÄòRockin‚Äô Chair‚Äô, and ‚ÄòStep Out‚Äô.

Reflecting on how Oasis made such an iconic album in a staggeringly brief 12 days, Noel recalls: ‚ÄúYou‚Äôre just working on instinct because you don‚Äôt second guess anything when you‚Äôre young. snippet.title: Need for Speed Hot Pursuit Remastered ‚Äì Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Reignite the pursuit in Need for Speed‚Ñ¢ Hot Pursuit Remastered, coming Nov. 6 on PS4, Xbox, and PC, and Nov. 13 on Switch: https://www.ea.com/games/need-for-speed/need-for-speed-hot-pursuit-remastered/news/announcing-nfs-hp-remastered

Ten years ago, Criterion Games released their critically acclaimed franchise debut Need for Speed Hot Pursuit. It introduced NFS and racing fans to the winding, open roads of Seacrest County, Criterion‚Äôs renowned feel for breakneck speed and gameplay, and the innovative Autolog system, empowering true social competition between friends. 

Ever since, we‚Äôve heard so many stories about the triumphant moments and heated rivalries Autolog fostered. Some of which run very, very deep. Like the one between Michael and Joseph. 

Now, it‚Äôs your turn to feel the thrill of the chase and the rush of escape in NFS Hot Pursuit Remastered, arriving to PlayStation¬Æ4, Xbox One, and PC on November 6, and to Nintendo Switch‚Ñ¢ on November 13! 

Unleash a savage sense of speed both as an outlaw and a cop in this timeless racing experience updated for today‚Äôs platforms. With cross-platform multiplayer and Autolog, enhanced visuals, all main DLC delivered at launch, and much more, this is the ultimate version of Criterion Games‚Äô critically acclaimed Need for Speed debut.

Pre-order now: https://www.ea.com/games/need-for-speed/need-for-speed-hot-pursuit-remastered/buy
Read the full announcement: https://www.ea.com/games/need-for-speed/need-for-speed-hot-pursuit-remastered/news/announcing-nfs-hp-remastered
NFS Hot Pursuit Remastered official website: https://www.ea.com/games/need-for-speed/need-for-speed-hot-pursuit-remastered/
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/needforspeed
Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/needforspeed/

About Need for Speed Hot Pursuit Remastered:

RACE YOUR FRIENDS WITH CROSS-PLAY AND AUTOLOG ‚Äì Bolt down the winding Seacrest County roads headfirst in racing that is socially competitive at its core ‚Äì now with cross-play support between PS4, Xbox One, PC, and Nintendo Switch! The groundbreaking Autolog connects you and your friends in head-to-head pursuits and races and instinctively delivers challenges based on your friends‚Äô activities.

ENJOY LOADS OF EXTRA CONTENT AND UPDATES ‚Äì Get all the additional main DLC delivered at launch including an extra six hours of gameplay and more than 30 challenges. Brand new achievements, wraps, car colors, reduced hard stops, an updated photo mode and gallery, and multiple quality of life updates create an even more well-rounded gameplay experience. 

DRIVE EXOTIC SUPERCARS WITH WEAPONS ‚Äì Drive the world‚Äôs most desirable supercars on both sides of the law. Bust suspects in supercharged cop interceptors enhanced with tactical weaponry, or level the playing field with counterattacks and defensive maneuvers as an elite racer. Strategize to gain an edge over the competition, no matter what side you‚Äôre on!

CHASE AND ESCAPE TOGETHER OR SOLO ‚Äì A deep and fully-defined single-player career delivers the action of both cops and racers, with a seamlessly linked multiplayer experience across all race modes. Take on friends or play through the career solo to earn Bounty and unlock new cars, weapons, and equipment.

EXPERIENCE A TIMELESS RACING GAME WITH ENHANCED VISUALS ‚Äì Need for Speed‚Ñ¢ Hot Pursuit Remastered delivers a timeless racing experience updated for today‚Äôs generation of hardware with enhanced visuals. Play in up to 4K/60 FPS and enjoy improvements such as higher-res models, shadows, and reflections, more objects and props, longer draw distance, boosted textures, more particles, and improved AA/SSAO.

‚ÄúWill you shut up, man?‚Äù Biden snapped at Trump at one point. ‚ÄúYou‚Äôre the worst president America has ever had,‚Äù he said later.

‚ÄúChina ate your lunch,‚Äù Trump shot back at Biden during questions on the economy.

‚ÄúI hate to raise my voice, but why shouldn‚Äôt I be different than the two of you?‚Äù the exasperated host said at one point.

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS | Liverpool vs Arsenal (3-1) | Premier League
snippet.description:
Our winning start to the season is over after Liverpool fought back to beat us at Anfield.
 
A bizarre goal from Alex Lacazette saw us lead the champions and lay the foundations for a memorable result. But our advantage lasted just two minutes as Sadio Mane and Andy Robertson struck to turn the tide in Liverpool's favour.

Diogo Jota then put the game to bed moments before full time with a crisp finish into the bottom left-hand corner. 

#arsenal #highlights #premierleague

snippet.title: President Trump and Melania Trump test positive for Covid-19
snippet.description:
President Donald Trump and first lady Melania Trump tested positive for coronavirus, the President announced early Friday morning, an extraordinary development coming months into a global pandemic and in the final stretch of his reelection campaign.
"Tonight, @FLOTUS and I tested positive for COVID-19. We will begin our quarantine and recovery process immediately. We will get through this TOGETHER!" Trump tweeted shortly before 1 am Friday.
In a memo issued to reporters around 1 a.m. ET, the President's physician, Navy Commander Dr. Sean Conley, wrote he received confirmation of the positive tests on Thursday evening.
"The President and First Lady are both well at this time, and they plan to remain at home within the White House during their convalescence," Conley wrote.

#Covid #Trump #CNN #News

snippet.title: Joe Biden and President Donald Trump spar in first debate: 'Will you shut up, man?'
snippet.description:
President Donald Trump and former Vice President Joe Biden face off in the first presidential debate Tuesday night, hosted by Case Western Reserve University in Cleveland, Ohio. For access to live and exclusive video from CNBC subscribe to CNBC PRO: https://cnb.cx/2NGeIvi 

President Donald Trump and former Vice President Joe Biden had their first chance to challenge each other face to face. They did ‚Äî a lot.

Hardly a minute went by in the 90-minute brawl without one of the candidates angrily interrupting the other, whether on the coronavirus pandemic, the Supreme Court, the economy or anything else, including each other‚Äôs families.

‚ÄúWill you shut up, man?‚Äù Biden snapped at Trump at one point. ‚ÄúYou‚Äôre the worst president America has ever had,‚Äù he said later.

‚ÄúChina ate your lunch,‚Äù Trump shot back at Biden during questions on the economy.

Even the moderator, Fox News‚Äô Chris Wallace, couldn‚Äôt always stay above the fray.

‚ÄúI hate to raise my voice, but why shouldn‚Äôt I be different than the two of you?‚Äù the exasperated host said at one point.

snippet.title: President Trump and Melania Trump test positive for Covid-19
snippet.description:
President Donald Trump and first lady Melania Trump tested positive for coronavirus, the President announced early Friday morning, an extraordinary development coming months into a global pandemic and in the final stretch of his reelection campaign.
"Tonight, @FLOTUS and I tested positive for COVID-19. We will begin our quarantine and recovery process immediately. We will get through this TOGETHER!" Trump tweeted shortly before 1 am Friday.
In a memo issued to reporters around 1 a.m. ET, the President's physician, Navy Commander Dr. Sean Conley, wrote he received confirmation of the positive tests on Thursday evening.
"The President and First Lady are both well at this time, and they plan to remain at home within the White House during their convalescence," Conley wrote.

#Covid #Trump #CNN #News

snippet.title: Israel Adesanya's Coach: Paulo Costa Win, Jon Jones Twitter Beef, Jan Blachowicz, Weidman, Chimaev
snippet.description:
In the aftermath of UFC 253: Adesanya vs. Costa, Israel Adesanya, City Kickboxing head coach Eugene Bareman speaks to Submission Radio about Israel's masterclass win over Paulo Costa, what's next for Israel and if he could realistically fight again in 2020, if the Jan Blachowicz fight could be a possibility, Israel's pec controversy, the recent Twitter exchange between Jon Jones and Israel Adesanya and why Eugene doesn't approve, what would have to happen in order for that fight to come together, Shane Young's opponent missing weight and why Eugene considers it the same as cheating, the punch mistaken for an eye poke in Brad Riddell's fight, and more!

1:20 How he grades Israel's performance over Costa
2:38 Paulo Costa's gameplan in the fight
3:58 What the gameplan was
5:56 If Israel's opponents are starting to get beaten ahead of the fight

9:30 The controversy surrounding Israel's pec
11:00 Why Israel has never taken any steroids

snippet.title: Need for Speed Hot Pursuit Remastered ‚Äì Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Reignite the pursuit in Need for Speed‚Ñ¢ Hot Pursuit Remastered, coming Nov. 6 on PS4, Xbox, and PC, and Nov. 13 on Switch: https://www.ea.com/games/need-for-speed/need-for-speed-hot-pursuit-remastered/news/announcing-nfs-hp-remastered

Ten years ago, Criterion Games released their critically acclaimed franchise debut Need for Speed Hot Pursuit. It introduced NFS and racing fans to the winding, open roads of Seacrest County, Criterion‚Äôs renowned feel for breakneck speed and gameplay, and the innovative Autolog system, empowering true social competition between friends. 

Ever since, we‚Äôve heard so many stories about the triumphant moments and heated rivalries Autolog fostered. Some of which run very, very deep. Like the one between Michael and Joseph. 

Now, it‚Äôs your turn to feel the thrill of the chase and the rush of escape in NFS Hot Pursuit Remastered, arriving to PlayStation¬Æ4, Xbox One, and PC on November 6, and to Nintendo Switch‚Ñ¢ on November 13! 

Unleash a savage sense of speed both as an outlaw and a cop in this timeless racing experience updated for today‚Äôs platforms. With cross-platform multiplayer and Autolog, enhanced visuals, all main DLC delivered at launch, and much more, this is the ultimate version of Criterion Games‚Äô critically acclaimed Need for Speed debut.

Pre-order now: https://www.ea.com/games/need-for-speed/need-for-speed-hot-pursuit-remastered/buy
Read the full announcement: https://www.ea.com/games/need-for-speed/need-for-speed-hot-pursuit-remastered/news/announcing-nfs-hp-remastered
NFS Hot Pursuit Remastered official website: https://www.ea.com/games/need-for-speed/need-for-speed-hot-pursuit-remastered/
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/needforspeed
Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/needforspeed/

About Need for Speed Hot Pursuit Remastered:

RACE YOUR FRIENDS WITH CROSS-PLAY AND AUTOLOG ‚Äì Bolt down the winding Seacrest County roads headfirst in racing that is socially competitive at its core ‚Äì now with cross-play support between PS4, Xbox One, PC, and Nintendo Switch! The groundbreaking Autolog connects you and your friends in head-to-head pursuits and races and instinctively delivers challenges based on your friends‚Äô activities.

ENJOY LOADS OF EXTRA CONTENT AND UPDATES ‚Äì Get all the additional main DLC delivered at launch including an extra six hours of gameplay and more than 30 challenges. Brand new achievements, wraps, car colors, reduced hard stops, an updated photo mode and gallery, and multiple quality of life updates create an even more well-rounded gameplay experience. 

DRIVE EXOTIC SUPERCARS WITH WEAPONS ‚Äì Drive the world‚Äôs most desirable supercars on both sides of the law. Bust suspects in supercharged cop interceptors enhanced with tactical weaponry, or level the playing field with counterattacks and defensive maneuvers as an elite racer. Strategize to gain an edge over the competition, no matter what side you‚Äôre on!

CHASE AND ESCAPE TOGETHER OR SOLO ‚Äì A deep and fully-defined single-player career delivers the action of both cops and racers, with a seamlessly linked multiplayer experience across all race modes. Take on friends or play through the career solo to earn Bounty and unlock new cars, weapons, and equipment.

EXPERIENCE A TIMELESS RACING GAME WITH ENHANCED VISUALS ‚Äì Need for Speed‚Ñ¢ Hot Pursuit Remastered delivers a timeless racing experience updated for today‚Äôs generation of hardware with enhanced visuals. Play in up to 4K/60 FPS and enjoy improvements such as higher-res models, shadows, and reflections, more objects and props, longer draw distance, boosted textures, more particles, and improved AA/SSAO.

snippet.title: In seiner Videobotschaft rutscht Donald Trump ein verr√§terischer Satz heraus: "Habe viel gelernt"
snippet.description:
#Trump #Corona #USA 
Der mit Corona infizierte US-Pr√§sident Donald Trump hatte am Sonntag ein Video in den sozialen Netzwerken ver√∂ffentlicht, in dem er zugab, einiges √ºber Corona gelernt zu haben. Das w√ºrde bedeuten, dass der Pr√§sident zuvor wenig √ºber das Virus wusste, an dem bereits √ºber 200.000 Amerikaner gestorben sind.
F√ºr eine kleine Spritztour im Wagen war er offenbar schon wieder fit genug. Trump hat am Sonntag f√ºr kurze Zeit sein Krankenhaus in der N√§he der Hauptstadt Washington D.C. verlassen, um aus dem Auto heraus einer Gruppe von Anh√§ngern zuzuwinken.
Zuvor hatte Trump auf Twitter ein Video ver√∂ffentlicht, auf dem er √ºber seinen Gesundheitszustand spricht ‚Äì und √ºber seine Zeit im Krankenhaus. Vor allem eine Passage stach aus Trumps kurzer Ansprache heraus.
‚ÄúEs war eine sehr interessante Reise, ich habe viel √ºber das Coronavirus gelernt. Ich habe es gelernt, indem ich eine richtige Lektion erhalten habe. Das ist die echte Lektion, nicht die Lektion, die man aus B√ºchern erh√§lt. Und ich kapiere es, und ich verstehe es. Und es ist eine sehr interessante Sache, ich werde euch noch davon berichten.‚Äú
In den US-Medien sorgte der Satz f√ºr Schlagzeilen. Hatte Trump gerade einger√§umt, dass er sich erst dann ernsthaft mit dem Coronavirus auseinandergesetzte, nachdem er sich selbst damit infiziert hatte? Seinem riesigen Expertenstab und mehr als 200.000 toten Amerikanern zum Trotz?
Die Kritiker st√ºrzten sich sofort auf den verr√§terischen Satz des US-Pr√§sidenten. ‚ÄûDas ist verheerend‚Äú, schrieb Antony Blinken, Berater des demokratischen Pr√§sidentschaftskandidaten Joe Biden, auf Twitter. ‚ÄûDer Zeitpunkt, um das zu lernen, war bevor wir 200.000 Tote hatten, nicht wenn es dich selbst betrifft. Wir w√ºnschen dir alles Gute, aber wir w√ºnschen uns auch, du h√§ttest deine Arbeit gemacht.‚Äú

snippet.title: Need for Speed Hot Pursuit Remastered ‚Äì Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Reignite the pursuit in Need for Speed‚Ñ¢ Hot Pursuit Remastered, coming Nov. 6 on PS4, Xbox, and PC, and Nov. 13 on Switch: https://www.ea.com/games/need-for-speed/need-for-speed-hot-pursuit-remastered/news/announcing-nfs-hp-remastered

Ten years ago, Criterion Games released their critically acclaimed franchise debut Need for Speed Hot Pursuit. It introduced NFS and racing fans to the winding, open roads of Seacrest County, Criterion‚Äôs renowned feel for breakneck speed and gameplay, and the innovative Autolog system, empowering true social competition between friends. 

Ever since, we‚Äôve heard so many stories about the triumphant moments and heated rivalries Autolog fostered. Some of which run very, very deep. Like the one between Michael and Joseph. 

Now, it‚Äôs your turn to feel the thrill of the chase and the rush of escape in NFS Hot Pursuit Remastered, arriving to PlayStation¬Æ4, Xbox One, and PC on November 6, and to Nintendo Switch‚Ñ¢ on November 13! 

Unleash a savage sense of speed both as an outlaw and a cop in this timeless racing experience updated for today‚Äôs platforms. With cross-platform multiplayer and Autolog, enhanced visuals, all main DLC delivered at launch, and much more, this is the ultimate version of Criterion Games‚Äô critically acclaimed Need for Speed debut.

Pre-order now: https://www.ea.com/games/need-for-speed/need-for-speed-hot-pursuit-remastered/buy
Read the full announcement: https://www.ea.com/games/need-for-speed/need-for-speed-hot-pursuit-remastered/news/announcing-nfs-hp-remastered
NFS Hot Pursuit Remastered official website: https://www.ea.com/games/need-for-speed/need-for-speed-hot-pursuit-remastered/
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/needforspeed
Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/needforspeed/

About Need for Speed Hot Pursuit Remastered:

RACE YOUR FRIENDS WITH CROSS-PLAY AND AUTOLOG ‚Äì Bolt down the winding Seacrest County roads headfirst in racing that is socially competitive at its core ‚Äì now with cross-play support between PS4, Xbox One, PC, and Nintendo Switch! The groundbreaking Autolog connects you and your friends in head-to-head pursuits and races and instinctively delivers challenges based on your friends‚Äô activities.

ENJOY LOADS OF EXTRA CONTENT AND UPDATES ‚Äì Get all the additional main DLC delivered at launch including an extra six hours of gameplay and more than 30 challenges. Brand new achievements, wraps, car colors, reduced hard stops, an updated photo mode and gallery, and multiple quality of life updates create an even more well-rounded gameplay experience. 

DRIVE EXOTIC SUPERCARS WITH WEAPONS ‚Äì Drive the world‚Äôs most desirable supercars on both sides of the law. Bust suspects in supercharged cop interceptors enhanced with tactical weaponry, or level the playing field with counterattacks and defensive maneuvers as an elite racer. Strategize to gain an edge over the competition, no matter what side you‚Äôre on!

CHASE AND ESCAPE TOGETHER OR SOLO ‚Äì A deep and fully-defined single-player career delivers the action of both cops and racers, with a seamlessly linked multiplayer experience across all race modes. Take on friends or play through the career solo to earn Bounty and unlock new cars, weapons, and equipment.

EXPERIENCE A TIMELESS RACING GAME WITH ENHANCED VISUALS ‚Äì Need for Speed‚Ñ¢ Hot Pursuit Remastered delivers a timeless racing experience updated for today‚Äôs generation of hardware with enhanced visuals. Play in up to 4K/60 FPS and enjoy improvements such as higher-res models, shadows, and reflections, more objects and props, longer draw distance, boosted textures, more particles, and improved AA/SSAO.

snippet.title: Deutschrap-Doku: Straight Outta Bornheim mit Celo & Abdi | DASDING
snippet.description:
Frankfurt Bornheim ‚Äì der Stadtteil ist in fester Hand von dem Rap-Duo Celo & Abdi. Neben dem FSV Frankfurt, Gentrifizierung, einem vielseitigen kulturellen Leben und der N√§he zur EZB haben die beiden hier die Base von ihrem Label 385id√©al aufgeschlagen. Wie keine anderen vereinen Celo & Abdi ernste Diaspora-Themen, mit Humor und Strassen-Erfahrungen. Celo & Abdi sind fest verwurzelt in Bornheim, haben die Multilingualit√§t aka Hinterhofjargon in Deutschland salonf√§hig gemacht und stehen kurz davor ihr n√§chstes Album ‚Äì Mietwagentape 2 ‚Äì rauszubringen. Sie verf√ºgen √ºber einen umfangreichen Blick auf die Frankfurter Rap Vergangenheit ‚Äì haben aber auch die Zukunft fest im Blick ‚Äì mit Olexesh und Nimo sind zwei starke Rapper auf 385id√©al gesigned. 


Unser Host Zino trifft Celo & Abdi und l√§sst sich von ihnen durch den Stadtteil f√ºhren. Er will wissen, wie sehr die Hood mit deren Rap-Musik zusammenh√§ngt. Die Tour geht vom FSV Stadion, √ºber der Geburtsst√§tte des Hinterhof-Jargons hin zum Platz wo sie ihr erstes HDF (Halt die Fresse) gedreht haben und endet in ihrem Lieblingscafe an der Konsti. Es wird mehr als deutlich, dass Celo & Abdi das Viertel, die Menschen, Rap-Musik und den Fu√üball in Bornheim lieben. Straight Outta Bornheim ‚Äì hier zeigt sich f√ºr Zino, wie aus Hood-Liebe Rap-Musik wird. 


Abonnieren und Glocke anmachen nicht vergessen! Schreibt uns in die Kommentare, wer f√ºr dich der Rap-Ehrenb√ºrger von Frankfurt ist.

snippet.title: Announcement of the 2020 Nobel Prize in Physics
snippet.description:
The Nobel Prize in Physics 2020 was divided, one half awarded to Roger Penrose "for the discovery that black hole formation is a robust prediction of the general theory of relativity", the other half jointly to Reinhard Genzel and Andrea Ghez "for the discovery of a supermassive compact object at the centre of our galaxy."

The announcement was made at the Royal Swedish Academy of Sciences in Stockholm.

#nobelprize
